,"typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"3c254cfc-beab-ffc8-0810-ffdca48f2df8","name":"Note: Daily Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Target Page\n\nGET https://example-market.com/posts — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Extract Listings (CSS) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"ccc24ee6-2e75-565b-327d-6f1c049a034e","name":"Note: Fetch Target Page"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Extract Listings (CSS)\n\nExtracts structured values from raw HTML via CSS selectors.\n\nNext: Rows from Arrays","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"f26543c9-9052-37ce-fb63-5dcbdf5ca8ff","name":"Note: Extract Listings (CSS)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Rows from Arrays\n\nCustom JavaScript: Zip parallel arrays into one item per listing\n\nNext: Diff vs Last Run","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"66d51b9a-1c96-f34f-6527-9a7dccb7228e","name":"Note: Rows from Arrays"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Diff vs Last Run · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,1030],"id":"f2c90c53-5eda-0158-89d5-2da59e75a6de","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Diff vs Last Run\n\nDiffs two streams by key into 4 lanes: only-in-A, same, different, only-in-B — the heart of the sync.\n\nPorts: ①→ Alert New Findings · ③→ Update Changed Rows · ④→ Write Fresh Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"b4adb1b0-f7e0-a119-c527-4d26ae61b574","name":"Note: Diff vs Last Run"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Alert New Findings\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Diff Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,40],"id":"e43aa624-8e35-fea2-a956-42141dad0e1f","name":"Note: Alert New Findings"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Update Changed Rows\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Diff Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,580],"id":"cff59d60-12ad-fd9d-4bc2-9b1af07ca65d","name":"Note: Update Changed Rows"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Write Fresh Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Diff Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1090],"id":"cdfabf26-c976-834a-49f3-02b8494f19ee","name":"Note: Write Fresh Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Diff Outcomes\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot 2","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"76478d27-75a3-bfce-490a-fdc0fcac8660","name":"Note: Merge Diff Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot 2\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"54cbe2fa-e526-ad9d-de91-29a14e768680","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot 2"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"4df60a24-76dc-0dbb-fdc7-6bd4e626712e","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"7ecf4317-ff2b-3339-87b5-bf26ccf0dd56","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"99d9f06e-8ad1-9a44-f1c1-df619bd1d95d","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"5adcec02-e8af-c479-c2da-25d441f9a2aa","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Summarize Run Stats · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"2892ae4e-a6d7-8921-dce0-4881aa4d171e","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,520],"id":"baefcc8e-95a3-c930-89c6-1dc8bf770b66","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,520],"id":"5d4f924b-aa52-4589-9def-a733b73544d2","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,520],"id":"37641c87-a511-9343-9d30-fbf4aec9b023","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6798,1540],"id":"bcfddbfd-9c12-f832-5dd5-3dae07fdbbe4","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `chatMessage` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7122,1540],"id":"99f92190-d687-5ab8-12a7-6c3e34108375","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7446,1540],"id":"a8f79684-c553-bec4-b2e0-13fd5055ac2d","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Track mentions of brand mentions with HTTP / REST API and Microsoft Teams\n\n**Pattern:** Social Listening · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nTrack mentions of brand mentions with HTTP / REST API and Microsoft Teams. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual engagement is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Fetch Target Page → Extract Listings (CSS) → Rows from Arrays → Diff vs Last Run → Alert New Findings → Merge Diff Outcomes → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to social listening without manual effort\n- Anyone automating engagement in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"548ff2ca-30c5-3471-b18f-77645c420767","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"5413c3df-96c7-8fa8-d4d2-6d8b51f97f2e","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"e4fbf762-fcb7-3400-338e-6633117b234e","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your engagement process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"2bced721-983c-5e64-944c-da12c6e690d6","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Fetch Target Page","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Target Page":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract Listings (CSS)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Extract Listings (CSS)":{"main":[[{"node":"Rows from Arrays","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Rows from Arrays":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff vs Last Run","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Diff vs Last Run","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Diff vs Last Run":{"main":[[{"node":"Alert New Findings","type":"main","index":0}],[],[{"node":"Update Changed Rows","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Write Fresh Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Alert New Findings":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Diff Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Update Changed Rows":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Diff Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Write Fresh Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Diff Outcomes","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Diff Outcomes":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot 2","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot 2":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Microsoft Teams":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"3542d233-e544-43bd-b0a7-d59098dfb628","id":"FDX07152"}